    <item>
      <title>お名前.comで取得したドメインを使用してACMでSSL証明書を発行する</title>
      <link>/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;表題の通り、お名前.comで取得したドメインを使用してACMでSSL証明書を発行する際のメモ。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;acmからパブリック証明書をリクエスト&#34;&gt;ACMからパブリック証明書をリクエスト&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112134641278&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134641278_hu3536da6bfd70b4ca6f30baa46cadec64_45948_6be02fcda99cfb9a6e2840c3488962ea.png 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134641278_hu3536da6bfd70b4ca6f30baa46cadec64_45948_2110d351becc9a1813634ef30821373c.png 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134641278_hu3536da6bfd70b4ca6f30baa46cadec64_45948_1200x1200_fit_lanczos_3.png 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134641278_hu3536da6bfd70b4ca6f30baa46cadec64_45948_6be02fcda99cfb9a6e2840c3488962ea.png&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;296&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ドメイン名と検証方法を入力&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112134754419&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134754419_hue3f3f1bef55f52be773db6b923560484_76098_497f58cb2dbbc5eba3fc9f9cbfec686f.png 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134754419_hue3f3f1bef55f52be773db6b923560484_76098_a0e13d45d0bbadf629276ba7b9bfebdc.png 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134754419_hue3f3f1bef55f52be773db6b923560484_76098_1200x1200_fit_lanczos_3.png 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134754419_hue3f3f1bef55f52be773db6b923560484_76098_497f58cb2dbbc5eba3fc9f9cbfec686f.png&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;596&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;証明書の発行中。しばらく待機する&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112134832140&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134832140_hu18765b1a39127ac83070f592d77700f2_49170_987df29d53167dc0d675f02f7cde601c.png 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134832140_hu18765b1a39127ac83070f592d77700f2_49170_3ffd3dd775ff6fdacd4fa6daace5079f.png 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134832140_hu18765b1a39127ac83070f592d77700f2_49170_1200x1200_fit_lanczos_3.png 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112134832140_hu18765b1a39127ac83070f592d77700f2_49170_987df29d53167dc0d675f02f7cde601c.png&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;123&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;証明書の詳細画面に移動して、「CSVにエクスポート」を選択して手元にダウンロードしておく。後続の手順で参照。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112135511287&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135511287_hudd2e64ed14c3aa649031b9b219e16484_140554_f3d1eda0fa4120395ed7d79f0bb92f60.png 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135511287_hudd2e64ed14c3aa649031b9b219e16484_140554_68ab117e7133053ce9212bd4ae5bc790.png 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135511287_hudd2e64ed14c3aa649031b9b219e16484_140554_1200x1200_fit_lanczos_3.png 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135511287_hudd2e64ed14c3aa649031b9b219e16484_140554_f3d1eda0fa4120395ed7d79f0bb92f60.png&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;303&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;お名前.comに移動して「DNSレコードを設定する」に移動&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112135631643&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135631643_hu2f041f787bad76babd8d3fe57bfa719e_53855_ba70e5594819a4a76edd71948ec4358f.png 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135631643_hu2f041f787bad76babd8d3fe57bfa719e_53855_b0fe5148ec2a4421e06bec52fa89d4c7.png 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135631643_hu2f041f787bad76babd8d3fe57bfa719e_53855_1200x1200_fit_lanczos_3.png 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135631643_hu2f041f787bad76babd8d3fe57bfa719e_53855_ba70e5594819a4a76edd71948ec4358f.png&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;390&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;対象ドメインを選択して次へ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112135711384&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135711384_hu215b722069856d31d3b181fac86df9c3_48034_b2ef33786316893bf3b35f842bf610e8.png 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135711384_hu215b722069856d31d3b181fac86df9c3_48034_268d537bba5527a8925a1058c5a900bc.png 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135711384_hu215b722069856d31d3b181fac86df9c3_48034_1200x1200_fit_lanczos_3.png 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135711384_hu215b722069856d31d3b181fac86df9c3_48034_b2ef33786316893bf3b35f842bf610e8.png&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;457&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;DNSレコード設定を利用する&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112135824174&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135824174_hu1728637d176a0c16f4548d2cf806c13e_109623_40619f63fc7bcd0dedb1913d565a72b8.png 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135824174_hu1728637d176a0c16f4548d2cf806c13e_109623_d46766bb633113a29d6f2c02070faa1a.png 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135824174_hu1728637d176a0c16f4548d2cf806c13e_109623_1200x1200_fit_lanczos_3.png 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112135824174_hu1728637d176a0c16f4548d2cf806c13e_109623_40619f63fc7bcd0dedb1913d565a72b8.png&#34;
               width=&#34;665&#34;
               height=&#34;760&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ACMの画面から下記のようなCSVをダウンロードしているはずなのでここから下記を入力する&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112140655648&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140655648_hub7facb073b9f4343f3b6544473e44653_32310_cca4b8a0a8e80e59e70a03dcd996291c.png 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140655648_hub7facb073b9f4343f3b6544473e44653_32310_001a915da2faf994847f34a96cff08dd.png 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140655648_hub7facb073b9f4343f3b6544473e44653_32310_1200x1200_fit_lanczos_3.png 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140655648_hub7facb073b9f4343f3b6544473e44653_32310_cca4b8a0a8e80e59e70a03dcd996291c.png&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;163&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th&gt;ホスト名&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;TYPE&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;VALUE&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Domain Name&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;CNAME&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Record Value&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;入力して追加する&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112140548910&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140548910_hua49e7058e6c39f85d2c42761b7126e06_23126_440a17562b64d176d1b840884776243b.png 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140548910_hua49e7058e6c39f85d2c42761b7126e06_23126_7e452781300275a4562108b93059810a.png 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140548910_hua49e7058e6c39f85d2c42761b7126e06_23126_1200x1200_fit_lanczos_3.png 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140548910_hua49e7058e6c39f85d2c42761b7126e06_23126_440a17562b64d176d1b840884776243b.png&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;215&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ページ下部の設定はデフォルトのままチェックを付ける&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112140711412&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140711412_hu6132eaee5451fc3810edc6d77f2aa09e_38743_dc92d760bef275750ab643d06b99a887.png 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140711412_hu6132eaee5451fc3810edc6d77f2aa09e_38743_d7d67dfed638b33f81d625d04dde2c0a.png 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140711412_hu6132eaee5451fc3810edc6d77f2aa09e_38743_1200x1200_fit_lanczos_3.png 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140711412_hu6132eaee5451fc3810edc6d77f2aa09e_38743_dc92d760bef275750ab643d06b99a887.png&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;257&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;設定するをクリック&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112140751547&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140751547_hu731891c9259de06080ff725042aa6a75_63950_6213d7b8e4f346316bf56642f5d4a7e7.png 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140751547_hu731891c9259de06080ff725042aa6a75_63950_45f444acf0e414979c991d58be990440.png 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140751547_hu731891c9259de06080ff725042aa6a75_63950_1200x1200_fit_lanczos_3.png 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140751547_hu731891c9259de06080ff725042aa6a75_63950_6213d7b8e4f346316bf56642f5d4a7e7.png&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;687&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;完了となる&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112140823966&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140823966_hu8eb668ebc65ce35502165ac8f9e380c0_13532_35f660be1f32bd8a24a82bafbcb0a09a.png 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140823966_hu8eb668ebc65ce35502165ac8f9e380c0_13532_49132d72b604090782065bcf899f4918.png 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140823966_hu8eb668ebc65ce35502165ac8f9e380c0_13532_1200x1200_fit_lanczos_3.png 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112140823966_hu8eb668ebc65ce35502165ac8f9e380c0_13532_35f660be1f32bd8a24a82bafbcb0a09a.png&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;121&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;数時間から24時間程度と書かれているのでDNSの伝搬に時間が掛かるので気長に待つ。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://help.onamae.com/answer/8081&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;https://help.onamae.com/answer/8081&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112141220725&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112141220725_hufed71dfcfa9a370a2c6691afa5f2edfb_82958_97e3e1582fbe021be66fe5399c1b71e5.png 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112141220725_hufed71dfcfa9a370a2c6691afa5f2edfb_82958_3f900eb0690740dec533c5449d21fa47.png 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112141220725_hufed71dfcfa9a370a2c6691afa5f2edfb_82958_1200x1200_fit_lanczos_3.png 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112141220725_hufed71dfcfa9a370a2c6691afa5f2edfb_82958_97e3e1582fbe021be66fe5399c1b71e5.png&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;436&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;数十分でステータスが発行済に変更になった&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;image-20220112142634611&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112142634611_hu8f247dc7b2ed912aa7dfae59c851bfd4_1672063_73b50edfaaad17adda4fac8a2c84b40f.jpg 400w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112142634611_hu8f247dc7b2ed912aa7dfae59c851bfd4_1672063_663af49690bc48c5bd9d0975abc1e8aa.jpg 760w,
               /aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112142634611_hu8f247dc7b2ed912aa7dfae59c851bfd4_1672063_1200x1200_fit_q75_lanczos.jpg 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;/aws-acm-ssl-certigication-setting/image-20220112142634611_hu8f247dc7b2ed912aa7dfae59c851bfd4_1672063_73b50edfaaad17adda4fac8a2c84b40f.jpg&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;90&#34;
               loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-zoomable /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
